➜广东诗人小隐：醉花阴.围炉煮酒
http://www.sohu.com/a/421210742_100115135	29281
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200927/97cc686f9cc34b15a09201bf775b665e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>醉花阴.围炉煮酒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">春来秋去无寻处，时序非言语。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">惊梦暗销魂，何必悲欢，老酒邀人煮。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">劝君不若花间数，篱落深深路。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">携手对东风，句子由衷，共把深情住。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200927/6224086868344422b0920490be853e63.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>小隐，自由职业者，一个游走人间的过客，喜欢用文字与灵魂对话的小女人，左手柴米油盐酱拌醋～右手诗词歌赋花间茶～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200927/92d92e417eac4e138299f8bfa0d33221.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
